{"tid":2238910,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"潘母：港府將曉穎當波踢  陳同佳案一周無進展 促管浩鳴勿拖延","createTime":"2020-10-11T13:27:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-12T04:30:00.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"7938bbc05d2bbe77846303f98384ec8b18f205e7","tid":2238910,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-11T13:27:49.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201011/WUIBCFUXYFFGFLTXYJRLX6AOV4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201011%2FWUIBCFUXYFFGFLTXYJRLX6AOV4%2F&d=bDSN5K49m9pAVz54ArwUlZq%2FK6ZSh20SQa5bazxoXL8%3D&h=5383f8f8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201011%2FWUIBCFUXYFFGFLTXYJRLX6AOV4%2F&h=d3ec38a8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201011/WUIBCFUXYFFGFLTXYJRLX6AOV4/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n潘母：港府將曉穎當波踢 <br />\n陳同佳案一周無進展 促管浩鳴勿拖延<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/l4IZfGaF_IFqbKuVpDT3w30YsAM=/1772x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/L3BSMIJBMBHOXNNVYTG3Q44XBA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fl4IZfGaF_IFqbKuVpDT3w30YsAM%3D%2F1772x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FL3BSMIJBMBHOXNNVYTG3Q44XBA.jpg&h=6e1fa82e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■潘曉穎母親昨指終於醒覺，轟港府將女兒案件踢來踢去。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】涉嫌在台灣殺死女友潘曉穎的陳同佳仍未履行赴台自首承諾，潘媽媽昨接受本報訪問，對保安局長李家超日前向傳媒聲稱陳赴台投案的主導權在台灣一方，「個波喺佢度」，潘媽媽聞言當場落淚，終於醒覺曉穎的性命對港府來說只是一個「波」，一直被踢來踢去。她又質疑，聖公會教省秘書長管浩鳴日前指陳同佳能否赴台自首即將明朗化，但一星期過去仍無半點進展，希望管牧或主辦陳案的台灣律師能交代事件，不要無限期拖延。<br />\n<br />\n陳同佳投案自首一事過去一星期再成公眾焦點，更引發台港雙方隔空罵戰，台灣行政院長蘇貞昌指，陳同佳不可以自由行身份赴台，促港府好好的談。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/NZ1_iQtc50OEUII5FkqbvVnH2Kc=/664x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/UCGI2QVD75HBPGP3DKMWNPIMHM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FNZ1_iQtc50OEUII5FkqbvVnH2Kc%3D%2F664x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FUCGI2QVD75HBPGP3DKMWNPIMHM.jpg&h=3039cf69&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■潘媽媽（右）與女兒曉穎關係融洽，自曉穎去世後，她大受打擊更患抑鬱症；圖為母女生活照。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n指不應再躲在安全屋<br />\n<br />\n潘媽媽昨日接受本報訪問，。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n當談到李家超以「個波喺佢度」比喻陳同佳投案一事的主導權在台方，潘媽媽痛哭落淚，哭稱此刻終於醒覺，原來對香港政府來說，曉穎的性命只是一個「波」，一直被港府踢來踢去。<br />\n<br />\n過去三星期，因女兒被殺情緒大受打擊患上抑鬱症的潘媽媽，接受本報在內多家傳媒訪問，公開要求出獄近一年的陳同佳履行去年10月23日出獄時許下的赴台投案諾言，更稱若陳同佳願意赴台受審，她會有條件為他求情，並質疑港府及警方有何理據讓他長時間入住警方安全屋，其後聖公會教省秘書長管浩鳴代陳同佳發出一段23秒錄音，指仍然願意赴台受審，管更稱已委託台灣律師跟進，但過去一星期事件仍無任何進展。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/Uk7LQQCWqsL2QFULeLrV_yGTKu8=/1195x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/ORRX5QLH2ZDZ7HT6EJEHZLS5HE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FUk7LQQCWqsL2QFULeLrV_yGTKu8%3D%2F1195x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FORRX5QLH2ZDZ7HT6EJEHZLS5HE.jpg&h=e8682aaa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■陳同佳至今仍未履行承諾赴台投案。"},{"pid":"d478dd2addf0383b0bb8ab14b35a1578d84fb806","tid":2238910,"uid":357031,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-11T13:29:57.000Z","msg":"請息懷 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1cefb48fb705ef9a51b9f460ea3464e181d815f0","tid":2238910,"uid":285514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-11T13:30:05.000Z","msg":"咁當個孫係咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59e2f753e32abd91de79d3cacd45a052ccc5f13a","tid":2238910,"uid":3457,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-11T13:31:10.000Z","msg":"你到依刻都唔直接講 政府當你地係政治棋子 你繼續唔識政治喇"},{"pid":"1a7b84f63a8911b6025c3af697d6247ce661e0c0","tid":2238910,"uid":186882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-11T13:44:32.000Z","msg":"難得一個人個女被殺最後無咩人同情佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bca1d1371fdb87a751584fddfe576880e3ba32bb","tid":2238910,"uid":61577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-11T14:01:40.000Z","msg":"一睇就知係垃圾藍屍"},{"pid":"9b02793e0398ff8182aa8b8132fa1c0ed096bece","tid":2238910,"uid":129924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bca1d1371fdb87a751584fddfe576880e3ba32bb","tid":2238910,"uid":61577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-11T14:01:40.000Z","msg":"一睇就知係垃圾藍屍"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-11T14:06:56.000Z","msg":"淨係知一定港豬到唔港<br />\n應該淨係為左返工 <br />\n住私樓但教到個女咁撚無品又無眼光<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9000da72163972c2b58ced04689a759b9c733e0","tid":2238910,"uid":209126,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-11T14:22:14.000Z","msg":"咁撚煩架呢條臭閪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你個女死係因為短命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"addb0f07a7cf12646af8ba0762415d6062b57a49","tid":2238910,"uid":235015,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-11T14:25:11.000Z","msg":"潘老母幾時死姐<br />\n真係好撚煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3214e34e31e6f46c405e7ccd5261e1d719e77f24","tid":2238910,"uid":318952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T04:30:00.000Z","msg":"唉叫佳佳殺撚埋呢舊膠佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}